structures, B3-3.3-02 self-employed Schedule C analysis with Form 1084 cash-flow addbacks for IBD hybrid advisors. SEC Investment Advisers Act of 1940 regulatory framework for RIAs, FINRA broker-dealer regulation, SEC Regulation Best Interest (Reg BI) fiduciary standard. Series 7/63/65/66/24 licensing context, CFP credential from CFP Board, CFA credential from CFA Institute. RIA channel growth and breakaway broker trend, PE-backed RIA consolidation activity (Hightower, Mariner Wealth, Captrust, Mercer, Beacon Pointe, Cresset), wirehouse forgivable loan recruiting wars, AUM-based fee model evolution, demographic transfer of wealth context." canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/sales-professionals/financial-advisor-sales/">
